			<content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/milestones/">&lt;p&gt;I have such lofty plans, optimistic timelines, and obsessive ideas… but I always forget about the finite resource that is time.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;future-plans&quot;&gt;Future Plans&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
