  &lt;li&gt;Get NN training/evolution set up with &lt;a href=&quot;http://lasagne.readthedocs.org/en/latest/&quot;&gt;Lasagne&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.delimited.io/blog/2014/2/20/fractal-ferns-in-d3&quot;&gt;Fractal&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/vicapow/d3-fractal-art&quot;&gt;visualization&lt;/a&gt; using &lt;a href=&quot;http://d3js.org/&quot;&gt;d3.js&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

